{"id": "1517512656070639788", "channel_id": "1517512656070639788", "author_id": "1505953646385565736", "author_name": "lost_in_the_mist", "content": "目前自己配隊的結果是340,最後一關借了+12茉夏\n\n目前我自己的配隊思路是從第五關往回配到第一關,找一個產銀鑰/盾的,主C,然後剩下挑能讓對手有負面效果的,但是我配完發現只有難4和難5打的比較順,其他都因為死扛,銀鑰和傷害不夠導致打的綁手綁腳,我想要盡可能的打更高分,想請教大佬有沒有更合適的配法?\n\n以下是我的配隊和box,然後印章的部分因為給阿拉刷入藥所以見底了:D", "timestamp": "2026-06-19T12:53:31.229000+00:00", "thread_id": "1517512656070639788", "attachments": [{"id": "1517512656809099374", "filename": "2026-06-19_202432.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2642313, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1517512656070639788/1517512656809099374/2026-06-19_202432.png?ex=6a39304b&is=6a37decb&hm=5a07afabf5f2413ba8332416daa9b46b066a2ff5bd19d2e0c42dac5afb4e9fb0&"}, {"id": "1517512657299701932", "filename": "2026-06-19_202441.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2704351, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1517512656070639788/1517512657299701932/2026-06-19_202441.png?ex=6a39304b&is=6a37decb&hm=7cda7e1f3f863555b1d154f068833dd08170f2ec8cb6bc24e76b3d60f4c121b3&"}, {"id": "1517512657899622480", "filename": "2026-06-19_202449.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2740106, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1517512656070639788/1517512657899622480/2026-06-19_202449.png?ex=6a39304b&is=6a37decb&hm=73955aec1446114d124aefb1339cefa7a7e7c6d1cfd29459faa34f006083ad00&"}, {"id": "1517512658461655161", "filename": "2026-06-19_202518.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2668612, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1517512656070639788/1517512658461655161/2026-06-19_202518.png?ex=6a39304b&is=6a37decb&hm=66c98e1b4fff9ec07c065321fce506f77c0ba4cf043fdeb125e3cf85bef014f7&"}, {"id": "1517512659036143648", "filename": "2026-06-19_202526.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2452601, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1517512656070639788/1517512659036143648/2026-06-19_202526.png?ex=6a39304b&is=6a37decb&hm=afdd826a0899efc925985bd90ddb38a79db